    <div class="local-box">
      <p>Melton is one of Melbourne's fastest-growing outer suburbs — and with that growth has come a large number of homes with wood heaters and fireplaces now several years into regular winter use. Many homes built here from the late 2000s onwards have flue systems that have never been professionally serviced. Cold westerly winds push through the Melton corridor from April to October, and heaters work hard. We service Melton VIC 3337 regularly — it's one of our highest-demand areas, particularly in the estates north of the Western Ring Road and around Exford Road.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY BOOK -->
