      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128168;</span><div class="rc-title">Weak or sluggish draw</div><div class="rc-desc">Fires that struggle to start or stay alight point to restricted airflow in the flue.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128197;</span><div class="rc-title">Pre-winter service</div><div class="rc-desc">Book in autumn before the heating season — easier to sort early than mid-winter.</div></div>
